description: Behind an ornate bar crafted of onyx and trimmed in gold, a dazzling array of flawless crystal decanters filled with colorful liquors have been displayed upon a tier of glass shelves.  An interesting sculpture of silver and wood that has been suspended from the ceiling serves to hold the snifters, glasses, and goblets used for the cocktails.
title: [Silken Mist, Tavern]
location: Silken Mist on Four Winds Isle
